                        <sf/>
                        <pf/>
                    </name>
                </names>
                <summary>Mrs. Catharine Noel, widow of John Noel and proprietor of the Golden Lamb
                    Hotel, died in Chambersburg at age 71. She survived her husband, with whom she
                    enjoyed almost a half-century of marriage, by two years.</summary>
