                </names>
                <summary>The German Reformed Sunday School of St. Thomas held a picnic in Gillan's
                    woods. A procession marched from the Church to the picnic ground accompanied by
                    the Citizens' Band of Chambersburg. Rev. Mr. Shullenberger addressed the crowd
                    of five or six hundred.</summary>
                <note/>
